  `clicks` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_commission` float DEFAULT NULL,

CREATE TABLE `sa_audit_inventory` (
  `id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL,
  `audit_quantity` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `current_quantity` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `pCode_wId` (`product_code`,`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `sa_audit_inventory_history` (
  `id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL,
  `from_pivot` tinyint(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `create_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `pCode_wId` (`product_code`,`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
